## Why Choose These Tiles?

Nobody enjoys standing water that can lead to slippery conditions and water damage. Thanks to the perforated design, these tiles boast superior drainage capabilities, allowing water to flow through effortlessly. This makes them ideal for areas where water accumulation is common.
